text: Franz Schediwy (10 November 1892 - 17 January 1960) was an Austrian football player. He played as defender for SK Rapid Wien. ==Honours == * 5 x Austrian champion (1911/12, 1912/13, 1918/19, 1919/20, 1920/21) * 2 x Austrian Cup (1918/19, 1919/20) ==References == Category:1892 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Association football defenders Category:Austrian footballers Category:Austrian football defenders Category:SK Rapid Wien players Category:Austrian football champions
